The sun blessed island located on the border of Turkey and Greece plays not so small role for millions of tourists every year. And especially this small island has to be awarded both for its historical heritage and its unique wild nature. From monuments and museums to leisure activities, this island is best place to start a fascinating exploration of the Mediterranean past.
